305
00:15:12,891 --> 00:15:14,031
Then I found out about that.

306
00:15:14,452 --> 00:15:15,312
Why did Rong insist

307
00:15:15,332 --> 00:15:16,411
on going to Shenzhen?

308
00:15:17,031 --> 00:15:17,852
Aren't there plenty

309
00:15:17,871 --> 00:15:18,992
