350
00:16:53,832 --> 00:16:55,112
Yes. Count me in.

351
00:16:56,671 --> 00:16:57,452
Another one for me.

352
00:16:58,391 --> 00:16:59,492
I'm a simple person.

353
00:17:00,131 --> 00:17:01,151
I'm thrilled that you

354
00:17:01,151 --> 00:17:02,051
