362
00:17:11,192 --> 00:17:12,912
All you know is to butter up your mom

363
00:17:12,932 --> 00:17:13,712
and Xiguang.

364
00:17:13,872 --> 00:17:15,652
Dad, aren't you used to it yet?

365
00:17:16,111 --> 00:17:16,652
Deep down,

366
00:17:16,652 --> 00:17:17,652
