367
00:17:17,952 --> 00:17:18,591
No.

368
00:17:19,111 --> 00:17:19,811
Not at all.

369
00:17:20,632 --> 00:17:21,291
Your mom

370
00:17:21,632 --> 00:17:22,472
is utterly wise.

371
00:17:22,771 --> 00:17:23,892
I am completely convinced.

372
00:17:24,111 --> 00:17:24,831
