00:17:36,212 --> 00:17:37,692
That's all for the first happy thing.

379
00:17:37,851 --> 00:17:39,432
Now let's talk about something else.

380
00:17:39,652 --> 00:17:40,892
Xiguang, Lin,

381
00:17:41,551 --> 00:17:42,652
I didn't have time

382
00:17:42,932 --> 00:17:43,851
