412
00:18:38,932 --> 00:18:39,831
I love seeing those.

413
00:18:41,492 --> 00:18:42,932
A local developer in Suzhou.

414
00:18:43,392 --> 00:18:44,640
The next few photos are too.

415
00:18:47,811 --> 00:18:49,751
It's still in Suzhou?

416
00:18:50,732 --> 00:18:52,331
